high_descs: Turn right and walk to the side of the white table on the right.
Pick up the knife with the yellow handle to the left of the tomato on the table.
Slice the tomato on the right corner of the table.
Turn right, walk to the stove on the left and look up at the microwave.
Put the knife inside the microwave and close the door.
Turn around, hang a right at the wall and turn right to face the white table.
Pick up a slice of tomato from the right side of the table.
Turn right and walk to the stove on the left.
Put the tomato slice inside the microwave above the stove, heat it, remove it and close the door.
Turn around and walk to the sink on the left.
Put the slice of heated tomato on the right side of the sink.
anns.task_desc: Place a slice of heated tomato in a sink.

high_descs: Turn left and go to the left side of the white table across the room..
Pick up the yellow knife no the left of the red tomato.
Slice the red tomato on the table.
Turn right and go to the front of the microwave above the stove on the left.
Place the knife inside the microwave.
Turn around and go back to the left side of the white table with the sliced tomato.
Pick up one slice of the tomato
Turn right and go back to the microwave on the left.
Remove the tomato after microwaving it with the knife.
Turn around and go to the front of the sink on the left.
Place the sliced tomato inside the sink.
anns.task_desc: Put a heated slice of tomato in the sink.

high_descs: Turn right, go forward, turn right to the table
Pick up the knife on the table
Slice the tomato on the table
Turn right, go forward, turn left and go to the microwave
Put the knife in the microwave
Turn around, go forward, turn right, go forward, turn right at the table
Pick up a tomato slice from the table
Turn right, go forward, turn left and go to the microwave
Put the tomato slice in the microwave, start the microwave, wait, pick up the tomato slice from the microwave
Turn around, go forward, turn left at the sink
Put the tomato in the sink
